ent-RMCSorokyneSign-name = Sorokyne landing sign
ent-RMCSorokyneSign-desc = A large sign that reads 'Sorokyne - СОРОКІНО - POP. 110' The Company logo is proudly emblazoned in the corner. Don't eat the resin coated snow.
ent-RMCSorokyneSignAlt-desc = A large sign that reads 'Sorokyne - СОРОКІНО - POP. 110' The Company logo is proudly emblazoned in the corner. Someone has crudely written 'FUCK OFF' in teal paint across the majority of the sign.
